'''''Alpha Kentrum''''' was a starship assigned to the [[Jedi geologist]] [[Michael Tandre]]. After he crash-landed on [[Orellon II]] and passed on the ways of the Jedi to the local [[Kentra]], it became the center of a holy temple built in his honor.<ref name="TP">{{JournalCite|2|The Prophecy}}</ref>

